Church CRM should contain and able to maintain the followng details
1) It should be able to store and update the details of the believers family.
2) It should be able to store and update the church employee details.
  2) a) Salary details
  2) b) Leave Details
3) Main Church booked and available details.
4) Marriage hall booked and available details.
5) Church Account Mangement(credit/debit). 
